data.description: Recently updated three-bedroom, one-bath home located in the heart of Rockport that is ready to welcome you home! There is great space for cooking in the beautiful kitchen and you will enjoy prepping food on the upgraded butcher block countertop. The dining & living areas can accommodate a variety of people. Bedroom sizes are great and there is lots of space throughout the property! Just step outside the French doors and you will be pleasantly surprised by the spacious backyard you will find. The large patio is a perfect place for entertaining with a huge yard for you to enjoy. This home is just minutes from all Rockport has to offer! Call your favorite realtor to see this home today!
